description: New Wave Holdings Corp. engages in the commercial esports/gaming activities. It acts as an investment issuer focuses on the psychedelic, natural wellness, and esports sectors. The company also provides investing and advising esports companies in business growth, market penetration, and product expansion; and financial information primarily to current liquidity, solvency, and planned strategic growth. The company was formerly known as New Wave Esports Corp. and changed its name to New Wave Holdings Corp. in May 2020. New Wave Holdings Corp. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
